text: Donald Trump, the reality-TV president, was a practitioner and a product of a style of pop-cultural grievance that will outlast him, our TV critic @poniewozik writes. https://t.co/GE89cEv8sT

name: nytimes
text:
RT @TaylorLorenz: Perez Hilton has been permanently banned by TikTok. 

I got the emails btw him & the company, which claims he violated terms “including posting content containing slurs, hate speech, sexual behavior, nudity, and bullying.” Perez says this isn't true.
https://t.co/nymR5naCyx
